Package com.hyleria.coeus.damage.kinds

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArmedCombatEvent
    Damage dealt between multiple people.
    DisarmedCombatEvent
    Damage dealt between multiple people w/o a weapon.
    FireDamageEvent
    Damage done by fire
    LavaDamageEvent
    Damage dealt by lava
    MobAttackPlayerEvent
    Whenever a mob attacks a player this event will be fired off.
    PlayerAttackMobEvent
    Whenever some player attacks a mob it will be ran through this event.
    PlayerDrownEvent
    As the player looses their oxygen they'll die; when they die this event will be fired off.
    PlayerSuffocateEvent
    When a player is stuck somewhere and runs out of oxygen you'll receive this.
    PlayerTakeFallDamageEvent
    Whenever a player takes fall damage this will be fired off.
    PlayerVoidDamageEvent
    When a player falls into the void (past Y: 0) we'll encounter this event.
    RangedCombatEvent
    Whenever players engage in combat using bows/other ranged weapons we'll hit this event.
    StarvationDamageEvent
    Whenever the player is deprived of food we'll start hearing this event be fired off.
